{"tid":1568312,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【團結誓言】平好少開POST，但今次要講淘大事件！","createTime":"2019-09-14T09:14:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T10:56:50.000Z","uid":62402,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"09eee28ae74a797fb5aec0a813a989ce4d439955","tid":1568312,"uid":62402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:14:05.000Z","msg":"首先，<strong>我在此向所有同路人立誓：不分化、不篤灰、不割蓆，團結一致對抗極權！！如有違此誓，孤獨終老、百病纏身！！</strong><br />\n<br />\n近呢幾日，不論係連儂牆被破壞，定係今日「淘大事件」都有兩極意見，變相造成<strong>某程度上既分化</strong>！！呢個現象唔好，所以我一定要開個post講！！<br />\n<br />\n一．「淘大事件」，對方抄我地行動，唔通我地咩都唔做?　<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>答案一定係要行動回應!!</strong></span></span><br />\n　　不過要<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>視乎情況</strong></span>，以及用咩<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>手段</strong></span>。今日既情況就係：當大部分手足都係天水圍既遊行既時候，藍屍廢老係淘大行動，以行動力黎講，手足要趕過去幫手已經有困難，更可況會分散遊行人數，所以一定要有<span style=\"color: red;\">「共識」</span>，否則會作無謂既犧牲！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以：</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong>手段1</strong>：如果以後有同類事件，Set一個時間點出黎，例如係1個鐘後，<strong>集合到一定人數</strong>就去聲援抗議！！<br />\n<strong>手段2</strong>：快閃制造混亂，佢地貪錢-&gt; 掉陰司紙。佢地愛國，我地可以<strong>掉傳單</strong>為佢地輸出革命、幫佢地平反六四等等。其他俾有更創意既你地諗。總之「兄弟爬山，各有各做」。<br />\n<strong>手段3</strong>：文宣，影相改圖，send番上大陸，係結構上瓦解佢地，都係個句俾有創意既你地諗。<br />\n<br />\n二．連儂牆被破壞，手足被襲擊要點?<br />\n　　見到人破壞，我地人多對方人少就上前阻止，我地唔夠人多就call馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n　　連儂牆可以再起，不過資源有限，所以要起，就起大範圍，周圍都係！！<br />\n<br />\n三．跳閘被捉點算? 緊係要走啦!!<br />\n　　1. 帶口罩先跳； 2. 健身；3. 搵手足一齊跳；4. 被捉就大叫幫手；5.手足見到有人被捉就上前幫手。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後，不分化、不篤灰、不割蓆，團結一致對抗極權！！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"4af0af384f550a1feb288b88bf979425a2d17030","tid":1568312,"uid":62402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:14:23.000Z","msg":"推!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"674cc409f9d87d36049862df013a86bcd1ddb434","tid":1568312,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:14:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d6083aea26b2b6d6d9e92617614abdd8374faa9","tid":1568312,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:15:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a722489ccde62725d1e2d36f42b3cc288510e433","tid":1568312,"uid":34144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:16:03.000Z","msg":"正解<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e28e2871fd549d1b630a070231338566b77e1e2","tid":1568312,"uid":53062,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:16:15.000Z","msg":"睇lihkg 互屌覺得灰心，其實出去一次就知係平行時空，企出黎的人好團結"},{"pid":"19a15cc09339ca24b73cc25f9076f3554a7e0a21","tid":1568312,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:16:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ed5b6bca8d6299c7f55ad46dd8687b2dcb7b52","tid":1568312,"uid":19294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:16:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dde866df7de5ff6ca9a448530f03cd4dcd972c1c","tid":1568312,"uid":19294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:17:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35bee20dbe0229e579f255a0081fcc79aa82cfa5","tid":1568312,"uid":224938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:17:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c84c7cd0fa38d3abffb2ce9e845d5b117d7ce269","tid":1568312,"uid":19294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:17:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a93de4a519e67eba7bbbec414b0becb8071f16cd","tid":1568312,"uid":181521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite